data.description: Step into this meticulously cared-for home, cherished by its original owner. Offering more than just newness, it boasts a welcoming, open layout with expansive living spaces. Revel in the warmth of laminated wood flooring throughout the living areas, while neutral ceramic tiles adorn the breakfast nook and kitchen. Retreat to the primary room conveniently located downstairs. Upstairs, discover a generously sized game room, perfect for family entertainment. The inclusion of solar panels for energy savings and water treatment for the whole house are fantastic additions, not only for sustainability but also for reducing utility costs and ensuring clean, fresh water throughout the home.  Enjoy easy access to 59N and Beltway 8, making commuting a breeze.
